1995;;Rough Magic;;British;;Clare Peploe;;Bridget Fonda, Russell Crowe;;comedy/drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rough_Magic;;The film is set in the 1950s and focuses on a pretty apprentice magician (Bridget Fonda) goes to Mexico to escape her fiancé, a wealthy politician, and to find a Mayan shaman who will teach her ancient principles of magic. She is being trailed by a detective (Russell Crowe) hired by her fiancé, a former photojournalist traumatized by what he saw in Hiroshima. He joins her in the search for the Mayan shaman, and falls in love with her.